    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在一场挑战您理智的惊悚旅程中，每一关都是一个等待解决的谜题，每一刻都充满令人不安的不确定性。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257160/extras/484e6dbde0c2357f32c2e7664a625109.poster.avif?t=1755164249\" width=800 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257160/extras/484e6dbde0c2357f32c2e7664a625109.webm?t=1755164249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257160/extras/484e6dbde0c2357f32c2e7664a625109.mp4?t=1755164249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您会发现自己被困在黑暗扭曲的梦境中，一个无尽的迷宫，昏暗的走廊和荒凉的房间似乎永远延伸。向前的每一步都犹豫不决，因为环境本身就充满活力，意图让您感到困惑和迷失方向。压抑的气氛沉重，阴影闪烁和舞动，看不见的角落里传来的每一次吱吱声和低语都让您感到不安。这是一个连空气都似乎充满恐惧的世界，问题不仅是您在哪里，而且是您是否真正可以逃脱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏受到经典密室诡异神秘的启发，将每一扇门都变成了一场赌博，将每个房间都变成了一场潜在的噩梦。有一种持续不断、无法摆脱的感觉，好像有什么东西在注视着您，总是潜伏在视线之外。只有偶尔传来的远处声音打破了寂静——提醒你并不孤单。生存的唯一方法是保持冷静，清晰思考，继续前进，但每个决定都感觉像是向未知迈进了一步。要小心，因为你并不总是知道自己要去哪里，有时，回头可能不是一个选择。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257160/extras/6c6a84a66a0a9c84d772d3fe9f054cac.poster.avif?t=1755164249\" width=800 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257160/extras/6c6a84a66a0a9c84d772d3fe9f054cac.webm?t=1755164249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257160/extras/6c6a84a66a0a9c84d772d3fe9f054cac.mp4?t=1755164249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能在为时已晚之前揭开这些不断变化的关卡隐藏的秘密吗？这里的动态难以捉摸，只有头脑敏锐、神经稳定的人才有希望毫发无损地通过。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你深入未知世界时，准备好失去方向感、解决神秘的谜题、面对你最深的恐惧。这不仅仅是一场游戏；这是对你的智慧和勇气的考验，挑战你在成为永远的一部分之前解开谜团。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257160/extras/5032751aab7ae2e52015a5112f5d49e9.poster.avif?t=1755164249\" width=800 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257160/extras/5032751aab7ae2e52015a5112f5d49e9.webm?t=1755164249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257160/extras/5032751aab7ae2e52015a5112f5d49e9.mp4?t=1755164249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
